data.description: Come and see this newly updated and remodeled home!  It is move-in ready and consists of 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and an additional outdoor shower. The upstairs loft, which is approximately 371 sqft, acts as a second bedroom and can hold 2 full size beds, sofas, TV and more.  An additional 216 sqft includes a covered lanai and outside laundry room which has access through the bathroom.  This impeccable home boasts over 1,300 sqft under roof and sits on 1 acre in the front of the subdivision, with lots of upgrades, including brand new:  ~ mold resistant drywall ~ on demand hot water heater ~ uv light water filtration ~ cabinets ~ countertops  ~ rain gutters ~ woodwork ~ tile and flooring ~ toilet ~ sinks ~ light fixtures ~ deck ~ raised garden beds ~ appliances ~ 10 x10 cemented dog kennel ~ catchment cover ~ rock covered driveway & much more.   The property also produces fruits and flowers such as oranges, pineapples, bananas, betel nut, coffee, guava, night blooming jasmine, roses, Hawaiian ti plant and more.   There is a 10,000 gallon water catchment, as well as an additional dog kennel, two plastic sheds, and an above ground pool with deck.  The deck and stairs were newly built and the back of the property was recently built.  There was an additional structure that the owners recently tore down due to safety issues.  The owners have put lots of hard work to make this place come back to life!  Just pack your bags and come to your new home.  All furniture is negotiable so there's no need to wait months on delivery.
